You need to add this to your application configuration:
---------------------------------------------

'modules' => [
        'menu' => [
            'class' => 'domain\modules\menu\Module',
            'defaultRoute' => 'menu',
        ],
    ],

---------------------------------------------

You need to add this to your application parameters:

---------------------------------------------

'menuTypes' => [
        'link',
        'tag',
        'content',
        'action',
        ],

----------------------------------------------
You need to add this to your composer.json

"paulzi/yii2-nested-sets": "^1.0",

